      "raw_text": "The plan now outlined for the\ncoast to coast automobile race in\nconnection with the Alaska-Yukon,\nPacific exposition is to have the\nrace start with the opening of the\nbig fair. Tom Moore, one OF the\nenthusiasts who is behind the race\nproject, looks for long list of en-.\ntries. The course has been deter,\nmined as far west as Granger,\nWyo., and the racers will pass\nthrough Buffalo, Cleveland, Chi.\ncago. Omaha, Cheyenne and Gran\nger."
